---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact | Thornveil"
  description="Contract engineering, technical advisory, IP licensing, agent products. Reach Jesse Morgan at Thornveil LLC."
>
  <section class="section-padding pt-32 md:pt-40 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full pointer-events-none" style="opacity: 0.05; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--color-accent) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

    <div class="relative container-max mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase reveal" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Contact</p>
      <h1 class="text-fluid-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-3 reveal reveal-delay-1">Inquiries Welcome</h1>
      <p class="text-base mt-4 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-2" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        Federal program offices, defense primes, evaluators, and prospective co-founders — direct line. Direct contracts open December 10, 2026 (DD-214). Conversations welcome now.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <a href="mailto:jesse@thornveil.ai" class="btn-primary text-base">
          jesse@thornveil.ai
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Typical response within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeranaias/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium transition-colors hover:opacity-80" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/thornveil-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium transition-colors hover:opacity-80" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/></svg>
          thornveil-ai
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider my-16 reveal reveal-delay-3"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background: var(--color-surface-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Conversations welcome</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            <li>Federal program offices (SOCOM, USCYBERCOM, DARPA, AvMC, NSA, AISI)</li>
            <li>Defense primes evaluating sovereign AI infrastructure</li>
            <li>System evaluators (review the public companions on the org)</li>
            <li>Senior offensive cyber operators (<a href="/cofounder" style="color: var(--color-accent);">co-founder track</a>)</li>
            <li>Federal procurement officers planning post-2026 acquisitions</li>
            <li>Press / analyst inquiries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background: var(--color-surface-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Company details</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Entity</span><br/>Thornveil LLC</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Location</span><br/>Tampa, FL</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">NAICS</span><br/>541511, 541512, 334511</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Founder availability</span><br/>Active-duty USMC; DD-214 Dec 10, 2026</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Org page</span><br/><a href="https://github.com/thornveil-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-accent);">github.com/thornveil-ai</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <div class="mt-8 reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background: var(--color-surface-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Federal acquisition posture</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Direct contract availability</span><br/>December 10, 2026 (post-DD-214)</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">CAGE / UEI / SAM.gov</span><br/>Registration scheduled for Q4 2026</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Set-aside</span><br/>SDVOSB eligibility under review</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Data rights posture</span><br/>Commercial item (FAR 12.212 / DFARS 252.227-7015)</div>
            <div><span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">Planned vehicles</span><br/>Direct contract; SBIR Phase I/II; OTA; CRADA; GSA/SEWP pursuit</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 font-mono flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1 text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase reveal reveal-delay-4" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">
                <span>jesse@thornveil.ai</span>
        <span class="opacity-40">&middot;</span>
        <span>Tampa, FL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  import Lenis from 'lenis';
  const lenis = new Lenis({ duration: 1.2, easing: (t: number) => Math.min(1, 1.001 - Math.pow(2, -10 * t)) });
  function raf(time: number) { lenis.raf(time); requestAnimationFrame(raf); }
  requestAnimationFrame(raf);
</script>
